Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我正在尋找的  也許就是另外的那個你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這片天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:16.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有一位擁有翅膀的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從很久很久以前就存在於那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:21.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到現在依然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:27.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在恆久不變的天空中  沐浴著清風展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽還沒能更加詳細的告訴我  就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.73,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從那以後  伴隨我旅途左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:41.00,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就只剩下天空中的少女的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和這個人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:45.91,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人也是在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.91,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你母親一直在尋找的那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算了  反正你不會是那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:52.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}飛上天空什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是誰都會有的空想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.35,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個女孩也會飛是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  她有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.68,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真好啊  我也想要一雙翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我回來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃閒飯的  給你個禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是樹懶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起那髒兮兮的人偶  這個可愛多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓你趕快賺到錢  然後就得請你離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.85,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}小   鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}工作後的美酒果然是再痛快不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感覺自己就好像是專門為了這個而活的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  吃閒飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今夜先從感動回憶告白節目開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己一個人玩去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了觀鈴  困了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…  可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  來我這  給你睡膝枕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:47.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了  又不是小孩子了  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎  讓她逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你經常讓她睡膝枕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}傻瓜！  開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子怎麼可能向我這麼不中用的人撒嬌呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她今天是否又說「嘎哦」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:17.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  她每次一說我就教訓了她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:24.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小時候不知為什麼非認為小雞是恐龍的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:28.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以在夏日祭的夜市上看到有賣小雞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說什麼也要買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過那時候我很窮買不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以自從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這孩子養成了動不動就「嘎哦」的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我根本不適合做母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果一直是一個人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:50.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再有  那孩子很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:55.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  她跟你在一起的時候  看上去似乎很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以的話就一直做她的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我已經無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來來  有趣的人偶表演就要開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:57.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好噁心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感覺會在做惡夢時出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  等等！  付了錢再走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}根本不行嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫土豆來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您的女兒還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  總是喊著大米好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃了一碗又一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這飯真的是沒有白做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:38.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請告訴她不要把肚子吃壞喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:49.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從剛才開始你一直在我家門前幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！  不許如此無視我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這不是土豆麼  在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你認識它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？  是往人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人在和姐姐說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  真棒啊  很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}土豆好像也成了往人的崇拜者了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是叫國崎往人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:23.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}技術雖然很棒  不過靠這種表演是賺不到錢的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到目前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可都是靠著這個旅行過一個又一個小鎮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:34.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎～  這麼說在這裏也賺了一大筆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？  說錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你想不想在這間診所中打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我叫霧島聖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自從父母去世以後  這裏的醫生就剩下我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直在找打雜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要砍竹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好開心  一直想這樣來一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼午飯會是流水細面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:09.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這個家中佳乃說吃什麼就吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼看這種座位分配都是不公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要怪你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰讓你看上去那麼貪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就明天同樣的時間過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}工錢呢？  到時候能多給吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:29.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就作為特別獎金  允許你在我家門前表演人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:33.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用擔心  午飯什麼的還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天真開心  往人咱們明天再玩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:40.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…看來我是找錯工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}話說回來真是個冷清的小鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交通事故一定很少…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意  撞到了你我也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過可真夠多的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為女兒喜歡吃米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且吃的很多  忍不住就買了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算是一點小小心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不…不用了 並不是為了這個才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那哪兒行啊  雖然不是什麼好東西  但也請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.59,Cookie,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(900,920)\frz338\fad(600,0)}香酥餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}難道在這小鎮上錢幣是不流通的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:32.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過那是什麼樣的女兒啊  能吃掉那麼多大米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是樹懶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}簡直就像個小版的觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不會是迷路的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又好吃又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是好吃還是可愛選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又可愛又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  往人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個女孩是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像是迷路的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}六歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好強的名字啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}名字是在年齡之前說的那個喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}志野彩香  六歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是志野家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.65,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:59.62,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她母親說那孩子不久就要去住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.63,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  好像沒那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:09.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還說有了那個樹懶陪著她沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.68,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.61,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.74,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這沒什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:22.87,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是一個不可思議的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:25.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一個天空的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.14,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己在天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是一個前所未見的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:39.49,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為這樣仰望天空的話  雲在頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:44.73,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過在夢中  雲卻聚集在我的腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.16,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}透過雲的縫隙可以看到大海的湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.92,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過卻不知道距離到底有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是一個無限延伸的廣闊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:03.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶  夢中的那個你  有翅膀嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.81,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個…  沒有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這種話還是不要對別人說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.71,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係  我只對往人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～  沒想到這麼合適
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剩下的全都是小號的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  很香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}便當  是我精心做的非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是你特意為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去把這個送給佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃今天在學校做飼養員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先說在前頭  若是敢在途中偷吃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會給您快速小心地送到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}{\fs52}可以跟房東說一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}{\fs52}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}學生還真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}補課的  社團活動的  還有委員會的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這兒的話也許能賺到錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}大家！  為我的人偶表演沸騰吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.51,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}YAHOH！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}國崎最棒！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.28,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}EVERYBODY SAY！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.66,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}國崎最棒！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}LOVING ME！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.49,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}國崎最棒！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…沒有這種可能性的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把這種怪異生物帶進學校的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒準學校就炸鍋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}除非我允許  否則待在這裏不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想請問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我來給一個叫霧島佳乃的人送便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道她在什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:54.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃可能還在醫務室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}醫務室…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:03.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不對不對  說是想吹吹風所以去了屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:07.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己嘟噥了幾句後就突然倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想只是有些頭暈而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣啊  往人為我擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的沒關係是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:27.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太誇大了  只是稍稍頭暈了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天空好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人不會飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼可能會飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是可以操縱人偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}毫不相干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你上次說過如果能用魔法會怎樣什麼的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  那件事啊  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我可以使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:51.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍稍誇大了點  確切的說是長大後才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:59.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過呢  我已經決定了第一個魔法用來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}秘～密～  第二個魔法的話可以告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也不是很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要嘛  問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:10.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不問我的話怪獸就會從肚子裏鑽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}人類會打不過它們而陷入大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個「地球地球！大危機！」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  「要保衛地球！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…好了  是什麼啊  第二個魔法想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想飛上天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}飛向天空的魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！  國崎往人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要發動突然襲擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:41.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}生什麼氣嘛  小滿特意叫你還不領情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真煩！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…腦漿在搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！  一個髒人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:54.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可憐啊  要在白癡主人身邊受苦是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說的這麼傷感！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  小滿來救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈哈  我走啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在這裏喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是搖屁股星人嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！  你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來追我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你給我… 適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  美風～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:35.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這不挺好  這樣還能讓美風幫你補補
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還不謝謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你驕傲個什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:39.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:40.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～  變乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  滿厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:48.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非常重要的人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}竟然隨時都帶在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:54.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到它就會想起珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:55.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許就像你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈哈  氣氛都被你毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:06.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}米票進獻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:12.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}遠野同學真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不光是學習  裁縫手藝也這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  咱們要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}人最多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:40.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那裏表演人偶的話  會有很多人過來看的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子到底是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是來神社參拜來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神社？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  咱們要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}馬上就是夏日祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時候就會有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會有很多小鎮中的小孩子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這小鎮中的小孩全是些傲慢的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:17.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都來到這裏了  我想再多玩會兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們來玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:23.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和往人玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}咱們都多大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那…  那咱們玩抓蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  有魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想捉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你倒是什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:49.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放暑假了嘛  想盡情地玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！  觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:55.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.79,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿～嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我走了  不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.38,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到現在依然相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小雞長大後會變成恐龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.98,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小雞長大了會變成雞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.38,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.73,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我真正想要的既不是小雞也不是恐龍的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽說你還為那事哭了一整天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:47.14,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼都可以的  只要是媽媽買給我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.67,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從沒過過如此快樂的生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天是你的生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:03.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這麼重要的事為什麼瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:08.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.33,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我若是知道的話  怎麼也會送你件禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大晚上的  有人會看人偶表演麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？  已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍微表演下給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過只憑這個的話  小孩子們是連看都不會看一眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:53.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去拜訪了一個朋友  不過她不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}作為給我表演了難得一見的東西的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:09.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真走運啊  拿到的正好就是蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:12.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且蠟燭的數目和我的年齡正好一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:16.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可能是想去給誰祝賀生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:20.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子不知道今天是你的生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣  滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那咱們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:43.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:45.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂～  佳乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又是神社…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像是進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:54.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:58.24,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}如同…星星的數目…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.72,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}山中樹木的數目…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:03.34,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}茅草…的數目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:04.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:42.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}干的活至少也該對得起工錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:44.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}土豆──
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:47.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}土豆──
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:51.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}法術…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:54.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世界上不可思議的事真多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:56.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她不總是做事怪怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算了  沒事就好
